{"tid":443694,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"『耳環撚』一人一隻字刻落耳環","createTime":"2017-10-21T19:23:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T03:48:05.000Z","uid":139913,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"60b74c86d599c039ae8e2d87ddacba92361121db","tid":443694,"uid":139913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T19:23:00.000Z","msg":"睇完曬使徒行者2<br />\n覺得比比鳥個耳環幾好睇<br />\n但又唔想買好普通個隻<br />\n想有少少獨一無二同代表到自己<br />\n跟住去左強國最偉大既淘寶搵到可以係隻耳環到刻字<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/22/031809_ea311cc74a57921e9dea62aadf01384c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F22%2F031809_ea311cc74a57921e9dea62aadf01384c.jpg&h=8be6a294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成品：<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/22/032015_ce2c8113220ffc49fba8b207bca3146d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F22%2F032015_ce2c8113220ffc49fba8b207bca3146d.jpg&h=e34e7526&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">懶</span></strong></span><br />\n依隻字最能夠代表自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc712eb1c835acc3126428083f07336ab2c9c47","tid":443694,"uid":90978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T19:30:59.000Z","msg":"五毛"},{"pid":"da8b2217b7dcf92a1e6cbebcf31fb150b7b38777","tid":443694,"uid":67289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T19:35:44.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"31f3a212be9cde403f9713c94b678ecf3306fdc5","tid":443694,"uid":145365,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T20:54:51.000Z","msg":"懶你老母咩 弱智死埋一邊啦"},{"pid":"5c598aee15174fe85070f8cbb93ac68aed4a1bab","tid":443694,"uid":115189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T00:07:21.000Z","msg":"好柒"},{"pid":"bbbe03a2a372d7d84eb42d7771f85da281bdb360","tid":443694,"u